                     <interp inst="t18510512-1144-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 1 hearth-rug, and other articles, value 36<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of Sir <persName id="t18510512-name-442" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18510512-name-442" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18510512-name-442" type="surname" value="CLAYTON"></interp>
